Let’s celebrate seaweed! 🌊💚🌏

Seaweed is packed with vitamins, minerals and antioxidants that are known to benefit skin and hair. It needs fewer planetary resources than land crops – and absorbs CO₂ faster 🌍

Our Seaweed & Citrus range is made with organic Scottish rock wrack, hand-harvested by teams trained to deliver high standards of environmental stewardship. Read more about the benefits of seaweed to skin and hair in our blog. Link in bio.
